cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with trajectory tracking of an unmanned quadrotor. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper proposes a hierarchical control scheme to handle the trajectory tracking problem. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the dynamic models of the quadrotor are obtained using probabilistic Gaussian Process models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a model predictive control approach for the quadrotor. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as computer vision techniques may be used in the quadrotor's operation.
